{"tid":2447777,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"創辦人涉「套丁」案被捕 滙豐拒認可王潘律師行","createTime":"2021-03-15T12:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T12:17:26.000Z","uid":85502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c05dd6aac3e067826c3bb367613717f4dd153aa1","tid":2447777,"uid":85502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:13:54.000Z","msg":"【新增滙豐回應】有「村屋大王」稱號的律師王光榮及其次子王德信，因涉嫌「套丁」，上周被廉政公署拘捕，而王光榮創辦的王潘律師行，今日傳出有銀行停用有關律師樓，而兩間龍頭地產代理行中原地產及美聯物業，均發出指引予前線職員，會協助有關王潘律師行客戶擬另聘律師處理樓宇買賣。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐發言人表示：「經最近重新檢視後，王潘律師行已不再是本行認可的其中一家律師行，能夠代表本行處理客戶的樓宇交易。我們將與客戶緊密聯繫以協助他們完成相關交易。承造按揭的客戶如有疑問，請與我們聯絡。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n創辦人涉「套丁」案被捕 滙豐拒認可王潘律師行<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210315/H4LGKC5KHBHJBKOZRSVAPW7WFU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210315%2FH4LGKC5KHBHJBKOZRSVAPW7WFU%2F&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDt4mdtfFL54JHswKolAMfW8%3D&h=c5ab3479\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210315%2FH4LGKC5KHBHJBKOZRSVAPW7WFU%2F&h=358a9e25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210315/H4LGKC5KHBHJBKOZRSVAPW7WFU/</a>"},{"pid":"2e607a21557bf34017342c087c7ede68cb856db1","tid":2447777,"uid":343754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T12:17:26.000Z","msg":"連燈仔: 鬥地主, 下年樓價跌9成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}